	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quomodo nostri cives tam in civitate quam ex agro proruerint in Gallicam militiam, proximis literis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Oben <ref target="file11984">Nr. 1937</ref>.</note> fusissime scripsi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed quid iam agendum est, quum res facta infecta iri<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>In der Vorlage</hi> ire.</note> non potest<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Adagia, 2, 3, 72 (ASD II/3 290-292, <ref target="file11315">Nr. 1272</ref>).</note>?</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person154">Myconius</persName> proxima dominica<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">6. Juli.</note> voluit illos decimare, Marcus<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Markus Bertschi.</note> contra illos fulminat in omnibus suis contionibus<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">suis contionibus <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note>, sed in absentes; Iacobus<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Jakob Truckenbrot.</note>, parvę civitatis<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Klein-<placeName ref="place97">Basel</placeName>, der Pfarrei St. Theodor zugeordnet.</note> pastor, totus caesareus est, omne malum illis imprecatur; si adessent, ne auderet mutire contra illos hypocrita.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego hactenus ne verbo quidem hac de re mentionem habui, quum me actum agere<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Adagia, 1, 4, 70 (ASD II/1 456, <ref target="file10402">Nr. 370</ref>).</note> sciam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam, antequam abiissent, tam audaces quidam fuissent, quo in officio cives mansissent!</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuum consilium hic requiro.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scio Davidem in hoc laudari, quod seditiosis pepercerit<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Vgl. 1Sam 24 und 26.</note>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reliqui iam consolandi sunt, quorum animos Gallicum aurum nondum tetigit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid camera a nostris pecuniarum postulet,<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><placeName ref="place97">Basel</placeName> hatte an der <placeName ref="place85">Badener</placeName> Tagsatzung vom 23. Juni mitgeteilt, es sei vonseiten des Kaisers aufgefordert worden, 6510 Gulden an den Kriegszug gegen <placeName ref="place11">Frankreich</placeName> beizusteuern; s. EA IV/1c 393 i.</note> ex relatu aliorum percepisti.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gliscit bellum crudele.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person1332">Caesar</persName><note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10"><persName ref="person1332">Karl V.</persName></note> non cessabit, donec totam <persName ref="person1332">Germaniam</persName> bellicis tumultibus involvat.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio in illius exercitu maiorem partem militum disenteria laborare, famem perpeti, nihil pecuniarum accipere et ex spolio vivere.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubi nunc caesar iam sit cum suo exercitu, ignoro<note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11">Der Kaiser befand sich auf dem Weg nach <placeName ref="place1660">Saint</placeName>-Dizier; s. <hi>Stälin</hi> 577.</note>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De ducis Brunsvicensis<note xml:id="fn12" type="footnote" n="12">Herzog Heinrich von Braunschweig-Wolfenbüttel.</note> exercitu<note xml:id="fn13" type="footnote" n="13">Vgl. unten <ref target="file12008">Nr. 1961</ref>, 22-25 mit Anm. 24; <ref target="file12016">Nr. 1969</ref>, 22-24.</note> nihil certi possum dicere, donec certiora cognovero.<pb type="edition" next="305"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libellus <persName ref="person138">Lutheri</persName><note xml:id="fn14" type="footnote" n="14">Das von <persName ref="person74">Gast</persName> gesandte Buch (s. oben <ref target="file11970">Nr. 1923</ref> mit Anm. 18) scheint also nicht Bullingers Anfrage (s. oben <ref target="file11905">Nr. 1859</ref> mit Anm. 1) entsprochen zu haben.</note> an extet, diligenter perscrutabor tabernas bibliopolarum.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum uxore<note xml:id="fn15" type="footnote" n="15">Anna, geb. Adlischwyler.</note> et liberis<note xml:id="fn16" type="footnote" n="16">Zu Bullingers Kindern s. oben <ref target="file11884">Nr. 1838</ref>, Anm. 19.</note>.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. Theodorum<note xml:id="fn17" type="footnote" n="17">Theodor Bibliander.</note> et Frisium<note xml:id="fn18" type="footnote" n="18"><persName ref="person69">Johannes Fries</persName>.</note> nomine meo salutabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bas[ileae]<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c">Bas. <hi>nachträglich eingefügt.</hi></note>, 11. iulii 1544.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus Ioan. <persName ref="person74">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem würdigen und wolgelerten hernn M. Heinrychen Bullinger, pfarhernn zuͦ Zurich imm grossen münster etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zurich.</s>
				</p>
